Author: ariaway
Text: tbh most people think ED is erectile disfunction anyway

Author: PhoneWalletSanity
Text: Don't worry. She might just think you're looking to lose a little weight or are curious about weight-loss. Normal people have no clue what EDAnonymous means and intermittent fasting and apps like loseit are very socially acceptable. That said, if you feel like you're spiralling into your disorder, please seek help; there's no such thing as not disordered enough or not displaying enough symptoms. A lot of the ED therapy I've been in didn't involve any forced eating or meal plans because it wasn't emergency treatment.
